    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, you actually believe that? You sound pretty convinced. Most people say regulation is necessary for things like safety or stopping illegal stuff, but you're saying even that's a violation. Can you explain why the argument for total non-regulation is more \"right\" than the argument for some oversight?",
